<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Paleness" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Paleness,</orth> wanness: <cit><quote>swooning p.</quote> <bibl n="shak. lc 305" default="NO" valid="yes">Compl. 305</bibl></cit>. == want of lustre or colour: <emph>thy</emph> (lead's) <cit><quote>p. moves me more than eloquence,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mv 3.2.106" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. III, 2, 106</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the p. of this flower,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.1.106" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A IV, 1, 106</bibl></cit>.
